  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nAt https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/master/packages/lodestar/src/network/peers/discover.ts#L53, I added:\r\n```\r\n    console.log(\"@@@ discoverPeers, maxPeersToDiscover\", maxPeersToDiscover, \"notConnectedPeers\", notConnectedPeers.length, \"time\", Date.now() - start);\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nin my environment, it printed out\r\n\r\n```\r\n@@@ discoverPeers, maxPeersToDiscover 24 notConnectedPeers 8092 time 1012\r\n```\r\n\r\nNormally it takes ~400ms but sometimes it jumps to more than 1s.",
