    "body": "I've profiled current master and this line seems to take the most time\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/0f5e44c8a114e4c8a490d82aaa7fd5c030f02a0b/packages/lodestar/src/network/peers/discover.ts#L47\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2021-03-24 09-08-26](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/112276190-c1cbe600-8c80-11eb-9578-5b9275a88b4e.png)\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2021-03-24 09-08-48](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/112276196-c4c6d680-8c80-11eb-8b55-f4291ee38d7c.png)\r\n\r\nThe issue is this line that will do crypto opts on all peers in the store (potentially 1000-2000 every heartbeat)\r\n```js\r\n    storedPeers.forEach((idStr) => {\r\n      peersData.set(idStr, this.get(PeerId.createFromCID(idStr)))\r\n    })\r\n```\r\nhttps://github.com/libp2p/js-libp2p/blob/b89445274d9a30beaa447a8ce05c2367109cc8a4/src/peer-store/index.js#L104",
